### HYMN LXXIX

#### A prayer for seasonable rain and prosperity

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0607901">1</span></span>May this our
Lord of Cloudy Sky, bedewed with liquid drops  
   preserve unequalled riches in our homes.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0607902">2</span></span>Lord of the
Cloudy Sky, bestow vigour and strength on our  
   abodes. Let wealth and treasure come to us.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0607903">3</span></span>Thou, God
bedewed with drops, art Lord of infinite prosperity.  
  Grant us thereof, give us thereof: may we enjoy this boon of  
   thine.

